      </gap>haritatem. <hi>The Gospel (saith</hi> Austin) <hi>doth not prohibit any <gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>hing more then incroaching co<gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
