         <g ref="char:EOLunhyphen"/>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>etousnesse, it enioynes nothing so much as dilating charitie. It is <gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap> poore center of a mans action, Himselfe. Jt is right earth, as a <gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
